reviews.review_text:
Dressed myself in green... Shoreline  ALWAYS GETS  ME  GOING....
just imagine outdoors...Sunny California...
 
just about this time of year...
 
BERTHA OPENER gets you passing the KIND to the hot chick next to you.start swaying back and forth and lo and behold you got a new friend ! 
 
..LET THE PARTAY BEGIN ! 
 
Kinda short show and a  2nd set "Touch" closer with a oh well US BLUES  Encore..but hey who's complaining...
 
you know Bobby's sportin the pony tail....
